r:#E1E4E8\">,\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">0\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">,\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">0.1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">);\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">  padding\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: \u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#79B8FF\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">rem\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">}\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"variable-fonts\">Variable Fonts\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>With the advent of \u003Ca href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Fonts/Variable_Fonts_Guide\">variable fonts\u003C/a> and better CSS support for typesetting, the web is finally catching up to print.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550684848-fac1c5b4e853?q=80&#x26;w=2070&#x26;auto=format&#x26;fit=crop\" alt=\"Abstract Shape\">\u003C/p>",{"headings":300,"localImagePaths":310,"remoteImagePaths":311,"frontmatter":312,"imagePaths":315},[301,304,307],{"depth":33,"slug":302,"text":303},"typography-principles","Typography Principles",{"depth":37,"slug":305,"text":306},"code-example","Code Example",{"depth":33,"slug":308,"text":309},"variable-fonts","Variable Fonts",[],[],{"title":287,"description":288,"pubDate":313,"category":187,"tags":314,"readTime":292,"lang":23,"translationKey":293},["Date","2024-11-15T00:00:00.000Z"],[291,109,56],[],"en/code-and-typography.md","zh/code-and-typography",{"id":317,"data":319,"body":325,"filePath":326,"digest":327,"rendered":328,"legacyId":344},{"title":320,"description":321,"pubDate":322,"category":187,"tags":323,"readTime":324,"lang":138,"translationKey":293},"代码与排版","展示我们如何在这个新系统中使用 Markdown 处理代码块和排版。",["Date","2024-11-15T00:00:00.000Z"],[291,109,56],"5 分钟","我们要以惊人的速度消费内容。但我们真的在阅读吗？还是只是在扫描？在这篇文章中，我探讨了数字时代排版对阅读理解和记忆保留的影响。\n\n## 排版原则\n\n在为网络设计时，我们必须考虑：\n\n- **层级**：使用大小和粗细来引导视线。\n- **对比度**：确保文本在背景上清晰可读。\n- **间距**：给元素呼吸的空间。\n\n### 代码示例\n\n这是一个 **TypeScript** 代码片段，演示了我们如何处理布局：\n\n```typescript\ninterface LayoutProps {\n  children: React.ReactNode;\n  isMobile: boolean;\n}\n\nconst Layout: React.FC\u003CLayoutProps> = ({ children, isMobile }) => {\n  return (\n    \u003Cdiv className={isMobile ? 'p-4' : 'p-8'}>\n      {children}\n    \u003C/div>\n  );\n};\n```\n\n以及一些 CSS：\n\n```css\n.card {\n  background: white;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n  padding: 2rem;\n}\n```\n\n## 可变字体\n\n随着 [可变字体](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Fonts/Variable_Fonts_Guide) 和 CSS 对排版更好支持的出现，网络终于赶上了印刷品。\n\n![Abstract Shape](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550684848-fac1c5b4e853?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop)","src/content/blog/zh/code-and-typography.md","7290c83b16c6d708",{"html":329,"metadata":330},"\u003Cp>我们要以惊人的速度消费内容。但我们真的在阅读吗？还是只是在扫描？在这篇文章中，我探讨了数字时代排版对阅读理解和记忆保留的影响。\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"排版原则\">排版原则\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>在为网络设计时，我们必须考虑：\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>层级\u003C/strong>：使用大小和粗细来引导视线。\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>对比度\u003C/strong>：确保文本在背景上清晰可读。\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>间距\u003C/strong>：给元素呼吸的空间。\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"代码示例\">代码示例\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>这是一个 \u003Cstrong>TypeScript\u003C/strong> 代码片段，演示了我们如何处理布局：\u003C/p>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"typescript\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">interface\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\"> LayoutProps\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> {\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#FFAB70\">  children\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#F97583\">:\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\"> React\u003C/span>\u003C